    'careers.business.advantage.title': 'What Sets Us Apart',
    'careers.business.advantage.paragraph1': 'Upvista\'s competitive differentiators are our R&D orientation and community ethos. While many competitors excel at execution, Upvista uniquely emphasizes emerging tech research (Project Cortex AGI, GCDF security) and open knowledge sharing.',
    'careers.business.advantage.paragraph2': 'We position ourselves as the agile, research-driven partner for ambitious organizations. Our approach combines "technology + design + strategy" integration, ensuring clients receive comprehensive solutions that drive measurable business impact.',
    'careers.business.advantage.paragraph3': 'Our commitment to digital literacy and social impact sets us apart – we\'re not just delivering projects, we\'re building a movement that brings change to society through innovation, inspiration, and transformation.',
    'careers.business.technology.title': 'Technology & Innovation',
    'careers.business.technology.approach.title': 'Our Approach',
    'careers.business.technology.approach.content': 'We use agile methodologies (Scrum and Kanban) for all software projects. Teams hold daily stand-ups and bi-weekly sprints. Quality is enforced by code reviews, automated testing, and documentation standards. We leverage DevOps tools (CI/CD pipelines, containerization) to speed deployments.',
    'careers.business.technology.cloud.title': 'Cloud Infrastructure',
    'careers.business.technology.cloud.content': 'We work with major cloud providers including AWS, Google Cloud, and Azure. Our cloud services enable organizations to leverage scalable, secure, and cost-effective infrastructure solutions.',
    'careers.business.technology.research.title': 'Research Initiatives',
    'careers.business.technology.research.content': 'Our research is the heart of Upvista. Project Cortex explores Artificial General Intelligence (AGI) inspired by the human brain\'s prefrontal cortex, while GCDF represents our vision for next-generation cybersecurity architecture integrating blockchain, quantum computing, cloud, and AI technologies.',
    'careers.business.team.title': 'Our Team & Culture',
    'careers.business.team.paragraph1': 'Upvista Digital is led by CEO Hamza Hafeez, who brings deep technical expertise and entrepreneurial vision. Under his leadership, Upvista emphasizes research-driven innovation and a culture of excellence.',
    'careers.business.team.paragraph2': 'We are building a core team of developers, designers, and marketing specialists, all coordinated through agile workflows. We follow "servant leadership" principles, emphasizing team development and ethical culture.',
    'careers.business.team.paragraph3': 'Our workforce is distributed globally, maintaining online collaboration tools for continuous integration. We cultivate a global community of contributors (developers, designers, engineers, forward-thinkers) via events and trainings, fostering collaboration and knowledge sharing.',
    'careers.business.cta.title': 'Join Our Digital Movement',
    'careers.business.cta.description': 'Be part of a team that\'s transforming industries and shaping the future of technology. Join Upvista Digital and contribute to innovative projects that redefine what\'s possible in the digital world.',
    'careers.business.cta.explore': 'Explore Careers',
    'careers.business.cta.positions': 'View Open Positions',
    
