    'careers.technicalWriting.culture.title': 'Work Culture & Environment',
    'careers.technicalWriting.culture.environment.title': 'Remote-First Writing-Focused Environment',
    'careers.technicalWriting.culture.environment.paragraph1': 'Our technical writing team operates in a remote-first environment that supports focused writing and collaboration. We provide access to documentation tools, content management systems, and collaboration platforms. Our communication emphasizes clarity, constructive feedback, and knowledge sharing.',
    'careers.technicalWriting.culture.environment.paragraph2': 'We have flexible working hours to accommodate different time zones and writing preferences. Core collaboration hours are 10 AM - 3 PM EST, but we understand that quality writing often requires extended periods of focused attention.',
    'careers.technicalWriting.culture.clarity.title': 'Clarity-Focused Culture',
    'careers.technicalWriting.culture.clarity.description': 'We foster a clarity-focused culture where precision, accessibility, and user-centric writing are prioritized. Regular content reviews, peer editing sessions, and user feedback ensure that our documentation remains clear, accurate, and helpful to all users.',
    'careers.technicalWriting.culture.collaboration.title': 'Cross-Functional Collaboration',
    'careers.technicalWriting.culture.collaboration.description': 'We emphasize cross-functional collaboration where technical writers work closely with development, product, and support teams to ensure documentation accuracy and completeness. Regular meetings, content planning sessions, and feedback loops ensure that our documentation aligns with product development and user needs.',
    'careers.technicalWriting.career.title': 'Career Development',
    'careers.technicalWriting.career.learning.title': 'Learning & Development',
    'careers.technicalWriting.career.learning.description': 'We invest heavily in our technical writing team\'s growth through access to technical writing conferences (STC Summit, Write the Docs), certification programs, and advanced training programs. Each team member has a personal development budget for courses, books, tools, and conference attendance.',
    'careers.technicalWriting.career.paths.title': 'Career Paths',
    'careers.technicalWriting.career.paths.description': 'We offer multiple career paths: Individual Contributor (Writer → Senior Writer → Principal Writer → Distinguished Writer) and Leadership (Lead → Manager → Director of Technical Writing → VP of Documentation). We support both paths equally and help you develop the skills needed for your chosen direction.',
    'careers.technicalWriting.career.onboarding.title': 'Onboarding Process',
    'careers.technicalWriting.career.onboarding.description': 'New technical writing team members go through a comprehensive 4-week onboarding program that includes documentation standards, tool training, and product familiarization. You\'ll be paired with a senior technical writer mentor who will guide you through your first documentation projects and help you understand our writing processes.',
    'careers.technicalWriting.expectations.title': 'What We Expect',
    'careers.technicalWriting.expectations.writing.title': 'Writing Excellence',
    'careers.technicalWriting.expectations.writing.description': 'Strong technical writing skills with ability to explain complex concepts clearly, create user-friendly documentation, and adapt writing style to different audiences and purposes.',
    'careers.technicalWriting.expectations.technical.title': 'Technical Understanding',
    'careers.technicalWriting.expectations.technical.description': 'Strong technical aptitude and ability to understand complex systems, APIs, and technologies to create accurate and comprehensive documentation.',
    'careers.technicalWriting.expectations.user.title': 'User-Centric Mindset',
    'careers.technicalWriting.expectations.user.description': 'Deep understanding of user needs and ability to create documentation that is accessible, helpful, and supports user success across different technical backgrounds.',
    'careers.technicalWriting.expectations.attention.title': 'Attention to Detail',
    'careers.technicalWriting.expectations.attention.description': 'Exceptional attention to detail and commitment to accuracy, consistency, and quality in all documentation and content.',
    'careers.technicalWriting.expectations.collaboration.title': 'Collaboration Skills',
    'careers.technicalWriting.expectations.collaboration.description': 'Strong collaboration skills to work effectively with cross-functional teams, gather information, and incorporate feedback to improve documentation quality.',
    'careers.technicalWriting.cta.title': 'Ready to Create Exceptional Documentation?',
    'careers.technicalWriting.cta.description': 'Be part of a team that\'s dedicated to clarity and user success. Join us and help create documentation that empowers users and drives product adoption.',
