    // Development Team Page
    'careers.departments.development.hero.title': 'Development Team',
    'careers.departments.development.hero.subtitle': 'Build innovative software solutions and cutting-edge applications that shape the future of technology.',
    'careers.departments.development.about.title': 'About the Development Team',
    'careers.departments.development.about.p1': 'The Development Team at Upvista Digital is the backbone of our technological innovation. We are responsible for designing, building, and maintaining the software solutions that power our clients\' digital transformation journeys. Our team consists of passionate developers, architects, and engineers who are committed to creating high-quality, scalable, and maintainable code.',
    'careers.departments.development.about.p2': 'We work across multiple technology stacks, from modern web frameworks to mobile applications, from cloud-native solutions to AI-powered systems. Our approach combines cutting-edge technologies with proven engineering practices to deliver solutions that not only meet current requirements but also adapt to future needs.',
    'careers.departments.development.about.p3': 'Collaboration is at the heart of our development process. We work closely with product managers, designers, QA engineers, and other stakeholders to ensure that our solutions align with business objectives and provide exceptional user experiences.',
    'careers.departments.development.activities.software.title': 'Software Development',
    'careers.departments.development.activities.software.desc': 'We develop custom software solutions tailored to our clients\' specific needs. This includes web applications, mobile apps, desktop software, and enterprise systems. Our development process follows Agile methodologies with continuous integration and deployment practices.',
    'careers.departments.development.activities.architecture.title': 'System Architecture',
    'careers.departments.development.activities.architecture.desc': 'Our architects design scalable and robust system architectures that can handle growth and adapt to changing requirements. We focus on microservices, cloud-native solutions, and distributed systems that ensure high availability and performance.',
    'careers.departments.development.activities.quality.title': 'Code Quality & Standards',
    'careers.departments.development.activities.quality.desc': 'We maintain high coding standards through code reviews, automated testing, and continuous integration. Our team follows best practices for clean code, documentation, and maintainability to ensure long-term success of our projects.',
    'careers.departments.development.activities.innovation.title': 'Technology Innovation',
    'careers.departments.development.activities.innovation.desc': 'We continuously explore and adopt new technologies, frameworks, and methodologies. Our team stays at the forefront of technological advancement, experimenting with emerging tools and techniques to deliver cutting-edge solutions.',
    'careers.departments.development.culture.remote.title': 'Remote-First Culture',
    'careers.departments.development.culture.remote.p1': 'Our development team operates on a remote-first basis, allowing you to work from anywhere in the world. We provide all necessary tools and equipment, including high-performance laptops, monitors, and software licenses. Our communication is primarily through Slack, video calls, and collaborative development tools.',
    'careers.departments.development.culture.remote.p2': 'We have flexible working hours to accommodate different time zones and personal schedules. Core collaboration hours are typically 10 AM - 3 PM EST, but we understand that great code can be written at any time.',
    'careers.departments.development.culture.collaborative.title': 'Collaborative Environment',
    'careers.departments.development.culture.collaborative.desc': 'We foster a collaborative environment where knowledge sharing is encouraged. Regular code reviews, pair programming sessions, and technical discussions are part of our daily routine. We believe that the best solutions come from collective intelligence and diverse perspectives.',
    'careers.departments.development.culture.innovation.title': 'Innovation & Experimentation',
    'careers.departments.development.culture.innovation.desc': 'We encourage experimentation and innovation. Developers have dedicated time for learning new technologies, contributing to open-source projects, and working on innovative side projects. We regularly organize hackathons and technical workshops to explore new ideas and technologies.',
    'careers.departments.development.career.learning.title': 'Learning & Development',
    'careers.departments.development.career.learning.desc': 'We invest heavily in our developers\' growth. This includes access to online learning platforms, conference attendance, certification programs, and mentorship opportunities. Each developer has a personal development budget that can be used for courses, books, tools, or conference tickets.',
    'careers.departments.development.career.paths.title': 'Career Paths',
    'careers.departments.development.career.paths.desc': 'We offer multiple career paths: Individual Contributor (Senior Developer → Principal Engineer → Distinguished Engineer) and Leadership (Tech Lead → Engineering Manager → Director of Engineering). We support both paths equally and help you develop the skills needed for your chosen direction.',
    'careers.departments.development.career.onboarding.title': 'Onboarding Process',
    'careers.departments.development.career.onboarding.desc': 'New developers go through a comprehensive 4-week onboarding program that includes system overviews, coding standards, development processes, and team introductions. You\'ll be paired with a mentor who will guide you through your first projects and help you integrate into the team culture.',
    'careers.departments.development.expectations.technical.title': 'Technical Excellence',
    'careers.departments.development.expectations.technical.desc': 'Strong programming skills, understanding of software engineering principles, and commitment to writing clean, maintainable code.',
    'careers.departments.development.expectations.learning.title': 'Continuous Learning',
    'careers.departments.development.expectations.learning.desc': 'Passion for learning new technologies and staying updated with industry trends and best practices.',
    'careers.departments.development.expectations.collaboration.title': 'Collaboration Skills',
    'careers.departments.development.expectations.collaboration.desc': 'Ability to work effectively in a team, communicate clearly, and contribute to a positive team culture.',
    'careers.departments.development.expectations.problemSolving.title': 'Problem-Solving Mindset',
    'careers.departments.development.expectations.problemSolving.desc': 'Strong analytical thinking and ability to break down complex problems into manageable solutions.',
    'careers.departments.development.expectations.quality.title': 'Quality Focus',
    'careers.departments.development.expectations.quality.desc': 'Commitment to delivering high-quality software with proper testing, documentation, and performance optimization.',
